    • Method Detail

      • getEntityRefsForSearch

        List<String> getEntityRefsForSearch(List<String> properties,
                                  List<String> values,
                                  List<Integer> comparisons,
                                  List<String> relations)
        Get a list of unique entity references for a set of search params, all lists must be the same size
        Parameters:
        properties - the persistent object properties
        values - the values to match against the properties
        comparisons - the type of comparisons to make between property and value
        relations - the relation to the previous search param (must be "and" or "or") - note that the first relation is basically thrown away
        Returns:
        a list of unique Strings which represent entity references

        Remove properties from an entity without wasting time doing a lookup first
        Parameters:

        name - the name of the property to remove, leaving this null will remove all properties
        Returns:
        the number of properties removed
